    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《符文竞技场》是一个拥有流畅战斗的决斗模拟游戏，结合了卡组搭建&amp;格斗&amp;roguelike元素，玩家将扮演一个角斗士，进入残酷的淘汰赛，只有活到最后的人才能成为冠军。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >QQ群 : 763229319</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/98c81f71018f7a390f15ead191927d0e.poster.avif?t=1767149454\" width=616 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/98c81f71018f7a390f15ead191927d0e.webm?t=1767149454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/98c81f71018f7a390f15ead191927d0e.mp4?t=1767149454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌握独特的战斗系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《符文竞技场》为传统的卡牌战斗提供了一种新的战斗方式：独立的队列系统允许玩家选择任意数量的卡牌，并且同时采取行动，卡组对卡组，而不是轮流行动。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/8e76a0d1d4a2510989997adb10a732dc.avif?t=1767149454\" width=616 height=156 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择你的战士</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从众多角斗士中挑选一名开始战斗，每个角色都拥有多种独特技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/614fc71831422719233633255caf7cec.poster.avif?t=1767149454\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/614fc71831422719233633255caf7cec.webm?t=1767149454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/614fc71831422719233633255caf7cec.mp4?t=1767149454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/416ba87320ebc3b4bcab24287e40e55c.avif?t=1767149454\" width=616 height=156 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >尝试各种武器装备</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尝试从战场上获得的各种武器装备。每件装备都拥有独特的技能，根据自己的喜好来搭建自己的战斗风格。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/a4d68d9893f0e034cc4eddb2e7b92569.avif?t=1767149454\" width=616 height=178 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >融合动作与魔法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将战斗动作与魔法结合起来，搭建自己的流派，用它战胜敌人。</p>",
